       IDENTIFICATION   DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID.      prog.
       DATA             DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE  SECTION.
       01 X             PIC S9 VALUE -1 SIGN LEADING SEPARATE.
       01 Y             PIC S9 VALUE -1 SIGN TRAILING SEPARATE.
